data.description: Gorgeous craftsman style dream home sitting pretty and private. This large luxury home has all the bells and whistles. Main level offers large master ensuite with two person walk in tile shower and laundry room for convenience, along with an office/study/flex room. Upper level boasts a large second bedroom. Lower level you will find 3 additional bedrooms along with an exercise room/flex room/additional sleeping space. Second living space with screened porch to take in the sounds of the rushing creek below. Enjoy your very own chef's kitchen with custom cabinetry and granite tops. 3 separate private porches and beautiful scenery from every level. 2 car garage, generator, and more! Gated community offers tennis court and swimming pool. Priced below appraised value!
